{"tid":1915039,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"濫權資料庫記錄1,700宗警暴","createTime":"2020-03-08T02:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T03:39:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ce5148d8f1af30a56d6618e77cd8b1cdb1cc28","tid":1915039,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:48:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200308/IWALWGLULMAFFZLKILRYQMTI7I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200308%2FIWALWGLULMAFFZLKILRYQMTI7I%2F&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5BwzJoBOSHi9wRld7hxL8G3jc%3D&h=c536b9f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200308%2FIWALWGLULMAFFZLKILRYQMTI7I%2F&h=df97414e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200308/IWALWGLULMAFFZLKILRYQMTI7I/</a><br />\n<br />\n濫權資料庫記錄1,700宗警暴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200308/large/1583599857_efe6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200308%2Flarge%2F1583599857_efe6.gif&h=bebf26fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港自6月爆發反送中運動後，警員濫權濫捕情況不絕於耳。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】在疫情影響下，香港的逆權運動雖有消退迹象，但3.5萬警員的濫權濫暴卻無休止。有網民自運動初期開始，蒐集傳媒曾經報道或只在網上傳播的警暴事件，整理成網上的「香港警察濫權實錄資料庫」，更將部份案例譯成英文和日文。由去年6月至今接近九個月，資料庫已收集約1,700宗案例。即使政權放生，世人不會忘記「黑警」惡行。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：擬增510藍帽子 議員斥打壓港人<br />\n<br />\n繙譯冀國際關注<br />\n<br />\n據資料庫數字顯示，香港警察的濫權濫暴明顯隨運動白熱化增加。資料庫在運動的首兩個月（6至7月），合共收錄129宗案例，到8月5日民間發起首次大三罷後，單單在8月就有超過208宗。到11月先後發生圍攻中大、理大事件，警暴事件更再激增逾一倍至440宗。武漢肺炎對運動影響循資料庫亦可見一斑。踏入1月，警暴案例有明顯下降趨勢。至2月，疫情在各區蔓延後，更下降至69宗，略低於去年7月。<br />\n<br />\n資料庫由自稱「90後IT狗」的網民C小姐（化名）發起，並與約30名自薦的網民合作管理、搜集資料、備份和繙譯，希望方便國際人權組織將香港警暴問題帶到全球，同時為香港民主進程留下歷史紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n■記者關冠麒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200308/large/1583599857_860f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200308%2Flarge%2F1583599857_860f.gif&h=d962c76f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"504fb254c09945b8a6efa24ca5b74e23f7a2dec0","tid":1915039,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:53:46.000Z","msg":"有冇咁少"},{"pid":"e8efd30c7a76da68e42474740b64a104c815fa77","tid":1915039,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46380d40befd158e46d4ca01c7762410a8ced4ad","tid":1915039,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:23:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab7a08d54d5dcf8ef4b08103637b4ddad1f4b40e","tid":1915039,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yxwqL4M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyxwqL4M.gif&h=b21f92f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7ac716a4745261e07567ef729f65a46c12b3ed8","tid":1915039,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:39:39.000Z","msg":"[推爆呢個post!] 大家一齊裝<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「爆門警報器」</span></span>幫唔幫到手足?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1915084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1915084</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}